title: I just literally took over 100% of my hp in damage from only Zed's Q
body:
https://i.imgur.com/E0My0kA.png[/img]

Thanks, series games, for bringing me quality matches when it matters most. I'm not really sure what to do when the game is only 17 minutes in and I get deleted from the game because Zed had over 10 kills by that time, but hey I tried my best.

On the bright side, this is the most accurate death recap I have ever seen.
